			<h2 class="body-current-exhibit">About the gallery:</h2>

			<p class="body-copy light grey">HUNTER+GATHERER designs and creates handmade furniture and decor blending art and function. Our mission is to explore creativity in a new way and inspire others by simplifying and streamlining designs.</p>

			<p class="body-copy light grey">We enjoy opening our doors to the public for the Arts &amp; Music Wedgewood/Houston Art Crawl each month and partnering with local artists to give them a space to share their work while also showcasing some of our pieces.</p>

